[Cite as 05105/2003 Case Announcements, 2003-Ohio-2219.]

May 5, 2003

MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

2002-1093. State v. Smith.

Cuyahoga App. No. 79527. This cause is pending before the' court as an appeal from the Court of Appeals for Cuyahoga County.

IT IS ORDERED by the court, sua sponte, that this cause be held on Proposition of Law No. I only for the decision in 2002-0201, State v. Fisher.

IT IS FURTHER ORDERED by the court that oral argument scheduled for May 13, 2003, be, and hereby is, canceled.
